        "fieldId": "9f94db6b-540e-4d62-85cb-c471f5908780",
        "content": "Trained at Tokyo\u2019s prestigious Tsukiji Culinary Institute and later refined under Michelin-starred chefs in Manhattan, Chef Sato brings over 15 years of global experience to our kitchen. His philosophy centers on *shokunin*\u2014the relentless pursuit of mastery\u2014and a deep respect for seasonal, local ingredients. At our table, he invites you to experience a dialogue between East and West, where umami meets elegance, and every plate tells a story of craft and care.",
